&lt;ul&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;It's been another few months, so I am providing another update. The standards council discussed that the GLUE working group has some energy and interests, and likely also needs some revitalization to continue on their activities.&lt;/p&gt;


	&lt;p&gt;Meanwhile, this document awaits integration of comments, and submission of a final version for standards council review. Please let me know if there is anything I can do to assist.&lt;/p&gt;    </content>
